AFME is also a member of the following:&#xd;
&#xd;
European Banking Institute, Institute for Fiscal Studies&#xd;
Joint Money Laundering Steering Group,	International Council of Securities Associations, Centre for Economic Policy Research, TheCity UK, European Parliamentary Financial Services Forum, European Forum for Manufacturing, CBI, Securities Houses Compliance Officers Group, Centre for the Study of Financial Innovation (CSFI), European Capital Markets Institute,&#xd;
QED, International Business and Diplomatic Exchange (IBDE)
